"ограниченный функционал. Удивительная эффективность."
msgstr ""
"This is a SaaS for small and medium-sized businesses. It does not require "
"integration into business processes. It is not a CRM or an autoresponder. "
"Artificial intelligence helps but does not replace people. Easy to use. "
"Sufficient but limited functionality. Remarkable efficiency."

